Build Instructions for zephyr

====================================================

(1) Prerequisites

    JDK 17+ is required in order to compile and run this app.

    zephyr utilizes Maven as a distribution management and packaging tool. Version 3.6.3 or later is required.
    Maven installation and configuration instructions can be found here:

    http://maven.apache.org/run-maven/index.html


(2) Build distribution packages

    Execute the following command in order to build the tar.gz packages and install JAR into local repository:

	# build zephyr
	$ cd zephyr/src/main/resources/static
	$ nvm use 22
	$ npm i && npm run build
	$ cd zephyr
    $ mvn -Dmaven.test.skip=true clean package -U
